{"tid":2236393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"賀錦麗(Kamala Harris)-slept her way into powerful jobs ??","createTime":"2020-10-09T12:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T12:48:51.000Z","uid":351574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10750fa7969ac6820b61acf4eb3b99a1e87fea52","tid":2236393,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.the-sun.com/news/1598547/willie-brown-kamala-harris-had-affair-san-francisco/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-sun.com%2Fnews%2F1598547%2Fwillie-brown-kamala-harris-had-affair-san-francisco%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=b83b9855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.the-sun.com/news/1598547/willie-brown-kamala-harris-had-affair-san-francisco/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snopes.com/fact-check/kamala-harris-affair-willie-brown/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snopes.com%2Ffact-check%2Fkamala-harris-affair-willie-brown%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=3f01438e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.snopes.com/fact-check/kamala-harris-affair-willie-brown/</a><br />\n<br />\nVice presidential nominee Kamala Harris had an extramarital affair with former San Francisco Mayor and State Assembly Speaker Willie Brown, who gave her two political appointments that launched her political career.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2020/10/07/kamala-harris-sexist-racist-attacks-spread-online/?arc404=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2F2020%2F10%2F07%2Fkamala-harris-sexist-racist-attacks-spread-online%2F%3Farc404%3Dtrue&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=3de261e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2020/10/07/kamala-harris-sexist-racist-attacks-spread-online/?arc404=true</a><br />\nAN EXCERPT FROM THE FACEBOOK POST:<br />\nWillie launched her career because she was having sex with him. The idea that she is an &lsquo;independent&rsquo; woman who worked her way up the political ladder because she worked hard is baloney. She slept her way into powerful jobs.<br />\n<br />\nSteve Baldwin, former California State Assembly member, Aug. 12, 2020"},{"pid":"5f24481806d0b62559022a0610fc92580087e53a","tid":2236393,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班女權撚仲撐唔撐佢"},{"pid":"0b69d8e9ce92a1449bb53da82c88ef69a783c4a6","tid":2236393,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f24481806d0b62559022a0610fc92580087e53a","tid":2236393,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班女權撚仲撐唔撐佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"性自主,要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f4177f58974c08c2ddb2dac08df29532c29971","tid":2236393,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"Willie Brown was 60 years old (still married)  and Kamala Harris was 29."}]}